name: Leak tray Multiphos 50 kg
description: Leak tray Multiphos 50 kg is mineral feed as a licking compound for cattle during the breeding season and for rations low in phosphorus. Is very well received. For rations with a low Ca:P ratio (0.8:1). The global licking compound provides the animals with additional minerals, vitamins and trace elements. Economical, strong, weatherproof. Without molasses = 100% minerals, does not attract flies. Product is swiss made.
